<li id="cite_note-Langbar.C3.B0r-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Langbar.C3.B0r_16-0" title="">^</a></b> Found in <i>Nafnaþulur</i> and <i>Óðins nöfn</i> (7)</li>
